      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is failing at runtime for me with:\n\n```\n  RuntimeException: Symbol$CompletionFailure: class file for NotNull not found\n  Caused by: Symbol$CompletionFailure: class file for NotNull not found\n```\n\nThe plugin jar is missing `org.jetbrains.annotations.NotNull`.\n\nOpenHFT `chronicle-values` and compiler POMs declare `org.jetbrains:annotations`[1] [2], but the built plugin JAR has no `org/jetbrains/annotations/*`.\n\nPerhaps we need to add org.jetbrains:annotations explicitly?\n\n[1] https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/net/openhft/chronicle-values/2.25ea4/chronicle-values-2.25ea4.pom\n[2] https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/net/openhft/compiler/2.25ea3/compiler-2.25ea3.pom",
      "revId": "235011a3be8467ba897a7122f97a62955063a1d7",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
    },
