      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thanks for the test. I assumed these annotation jars were only needed at compile time and excluded them from the final plugin artifact.\n\nIt turns out Chronicle Values performs runtime code generation/compilation, and that generated/compiled code references the annotations. So the annotations jar must be present on the plugin runtime classpath as well.\n\nDone.",
