      "writtenOn": "2026-06-03T17:34:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "How does one _merge_ the contents of the `MODULE.bazel`?\nJust _appending_ or there\u0027s any particular logic?\n\nSince these instructions are likely relevant for every plugin, is there some generic centralized documentation we can point to?",
